**This is my map for The Underwater Mystery Contest.**

_Ka Underwater Discovery - A Cs:s knife arena map._

_**Map story**_
===============

One day You and your buddies found a big hole with water in it in a forest. You thought it's a good swimming place. You dove underwater to check if it's a safe place. Suddenly you noticed astounding fishes, and you thought only you know about them. 
In the same time there went an armed people, and they knew about these fishes before. They propably want to get money on discovery them so when they saw your items at the edge, few of them dave underwater, and few of them stayed on the edge...

_**Gameplay**_
==============

You are with your buddies underwater (CTs) and you must kill enemies (Ts). You have only knife to use, because guns doesn't work underwater.

_**Notes**_
===========

Hope you like my map, I spent much time on doing displacements. Enjoy :)

This is ka_swamp. It is set in well a swamp. It's a fun map with a main level and an outer ring. 
------------------
There are some "gimmicks" in this map.
1. The red spinning orbs are "power-ups" which increase your speed to 130% there are only two on the map.
2. To prevent stupid stand-offs where nothing happens anywhere from 45-90 seconds into the map a large amount of grenades will fall from a glass box.
3. To force end the map, very useful if you are using bots who get stuck, the deadly gasses from the swamp will begin to take their toll on the players. 120 seconds into the map the gasses will begin to have their effect, they get deadlier over time.
------------------
Bots do not do very well on this map
------------------

Spawns, 20T - 20CT

INTRODUCTION
 Finally I can release a functional, good looking map. I have been trying a lot on soccer stuff, normally just did quick jobs, that weren't worth releasing them. This map was created for the extreme Soccer League, the XSL. If you haven't played soccer yet, search for servers with ka_soccer as map filter, it can be a lot of fun. The original stadium is the "Nuevo Estadio Independiente" in Spain. EDIT: THIS IS THE FIX-VERSION, CHANGES INCLUDE PUBLIC SERVER-FUNCTIONALITY AND BUGFIXES!
INSTALLATION
 Just put the ka_soccer_xslcentre_fix.bsp into your CS:S map folder, which is located at: ?:\Program Files\Valve\Steam\SteamApps\*STEAM NAME*\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps\ or similar folder structures.
ABOUT THE MAP
 The goal of the map is to use teamplay to score and assist goals. If you are alone or with a friend on the map, you can check out the training area to improve your skills or just take a bath in the whirlpool.
LAST NOTES
 If you find any bug, feel free to contact us. If you like this map, please rate it good and add it to your favorites. Oh, and please upload it to your soccer servers! Thanks!
